    Resource hints may also be sent in the HTTP response headers using the
    <code>Link</code>
    header. This works similarly to placing the
    <code>&lt;link&gt;</code>
    in the markup.
  </p>
  <p>
    This demo includes a
    <code>Link, &lt;https://cdn.glitch.global&gt;; rel=preconnect;</code>
    response header.
  </p>
